title: rabbitme
author: rabbitme
content: We are a team of people who want to create a crypto project. We are in the process of creation and we need people. The project will be a POW coin, NO premined, NO ICO... just Rabbit.If you are interested in development write to our account. We will publish more information soon, we are at a very early stage of the project.Knowledgeable people needed:- Community manager- Html, JavaScript, any language focused on web development.- C, C++, PythonRabbitGuardCoin your Rabbit coin!

comments.body: Hey! I am interested in your project and I believe our partnership can be mutually beneficial. If you are interested, please contact me on my discord here - https://discord.gg/4t4uYnU (AL1CE) Thank you.
